experiment heatncool
instrument VHF
start 2014 06 07 0900
end 2014 06 07 1100
status R
description Measurement of the D-region heating and cooling rates in a sub-millisecond resolution
contact Antti Kero
email antti.kero@sgo.fi
operator Antti Kero
submitter Antti Kero
resources FI(14)
notes
Measurement of the D-region heating and cooling rates in a sub-millisecond
resolution by superposing a sufficient number of short heater on/off modulations
together. Raw-data sampling makes the superposition possible.


